snippet: Penn State renewed its rivalry with Navy with a win before a morale-boosting crowd in State College. The victory was Coach Bill O’Brien’s first career victory.
abstract: College Football East Roundup; Penn State defeats Navy, 34-7, to record its first win of the season and coach Bill O'Brien's first career victory.
lead_paragraph: Penn State renewed its rivalry with Navy with a win before a morale-boosting crowd in State College. The victory was Coach Bill O’Brien’s first career victory.

headline.seo: Penn State Gives Bill O’Brien, and Fans, First Win of Season
headline.main: Penn State Gives Coach, and Fans, First Win of the Season
headline.print_headline: Penn State Ends Drought, Giving Coach His First Win
